               <persName>
                  <name type="gentilicium" key="Pupidia">Pupidiae</name>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Chrestenus">Chresteni</name>
               </persName>;
                    <lb n="2"/> vixit ann<hi rend="tall">i</hi>s <num xml:lang="lat" value="42">XXXXII</num>.
                    <lb n="3"/>
               <persName>
                  <name type="praenomen" key="Gaius">
                     <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan>
                  </name>
                  <name type="gentilicium" key="Cornelius">Cornelius</name>
                  <lb n="4"/>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Puteolanus">Puteolanus</name>
               </persName>
               <lb n="5"/> coniugi
                   <lb n="6"/> dulc<hi rend="tall">i</hi>ssimae
                    <lb n="7"/> fecit.</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>To Pupidia Chreste; she lived for forty-two years. Gaius Cornelius Puteolanus
               made this for (his) dearest wife.</p>
         </div>
